column5: ARE INDIAN RESERVATIONS (WATER) OFF LIMITS TO FISHING? SPECIFICALLY, OTTER TAIL OFF OF RED GUT BAY. MY PARTY WILL FISH THE RED GUT AREA BEGINNING OF JULY, ALSO FISHED LAST YEAR. ALSO, HOW'S THE FISHING AROUND DEER ISLAND? WE STAY AT THE FISHERIES RESORT. THANKS IN ADVANCE.
No it isn't closed. Fishing around the island is good.
